title: Jhong Xing Su Shih
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Buffet, Fast food, Take-out, Taiwanese
description: A small lunch & dinner buffet spread. Food is brought out prior to 10:30 so only a couple dishes may be hot. Brown rice available. Pay by weight. Note that the faux meats might contain dairy/whey. This area is loaded with small veggie places. Explore south further down Zhongmei St and the side alleys.
